Name: Tomb Of Pharaohs
About the game: Collect keys to unlock the 'Pharaohs Tomb' and fight his remains to pass the level! Dodge traps, scorpions and mummies in a procedurally generated maze with an infinite amount of levels. Collect coins to unlock characters, upgrade them and increase rewards! How deep into the tomb you can go?
